5:
Alk! What about over there? Did you
find Telluna?
9:
No, and she hasn't returned to
Starview either... Where could she be?
13:
I just hope that she hasn't been
caught up in any dangerous
situations...
25:
Telluna?! What is the meaning of
this?!
32:
Ah, Alk and Light! Welcome to the
shop! Are you looking for anything in
particular?
42:
I'm working at this shop right now! At
least until Mr. Thief comes back!
48:
Er, care to elaborate on that last
part?
65:
Th-thank you, young lady!
Now... you! Cough up what you stole
this instant!
67:
I-I-I'm so, so, so sorry! I don't know
what came over me! I just saw that
beautiful hair accessory and HAD to
have it...
69:
Y-you see, my family is going
through hard times... *sniff* I just
wanted to get my lovely daughter a
present to make it up to her!
73:
I-is that true?! Oh... I had no idea!
*sniff* Aww... that's so sad!
77:
But it's not an excuse to steal, you
know! Your daughter wouldn't be
happy knowing her present was
stolen...
80:
She's right, you know! Now, come on!
I'm turning you in!
82:
W-wait! At least let me say goodbye
to my daughter!
85: Um, wait, sir! I think I have an idea!
90:
So you offered to help out at the
shop until that thief returns...
96:
That's right. I figured his daughter
would be worried if her father
suddenly disappeared...
101:
Well, I'm sure that's true, but... How
do I put this...
104:
Are these people friends of yours,
young lady? In that case, why don't
you head home now? Thanks for
your help today.
107:
Huh? B-but that man hasn't come
back yet!
110:
And he's not going to... You were
tricked.
114:
W-we don't know that for sure yet!
At least let me help out until close!
Please!
117:
If that's what you want, I won't stop
you... But don't get your hopes up.
124:
Sorry about this, but I can't go home
just yet. You guys can go back
without me.
128:
Actually, why don't we help out as
well? Working a job you're unfamiliar
with must be difficult alone.
133:
Yeah, and we already finished what
we were doing here, so we're free for
the rest of the day.
137:
Th-thank you! Then let's all wait for
Mr. Thief together!
144:
I had hoped to be proven wrong,
but... It looks like that man won't be
returning...
148:
I'm sorry you two got sucked into
this mess with me...
153:
Come on, we're the ones who
offered, right? You don't need to
apologize.
156:
It is a bit disappointing though, isn't
it?
161:
Telluna, that kind heart of yours is a
rare virtue, but remember that too
much of anything is bad for you.
Even kindness.
169:
But... If the same thing happened
again, I think I'd still believe him.
173:
I'd rather be tricked than ignore
someone who might be in need!
176:
Besides, I'm a pretty simple person.
Even if I'm disappointed he didn't
return, that'll go away with a good
night's sleep! So you don't need to
worry about me.
184:
Well, the shop's all closed up. Good
work out there, little lady. You can
head home now.
191:
You don't need to apologize. Having
such a cute poster girl for the day
really helped my sales!
193:
Don't you worry your little head
about me. Ah, it's not much, but take
these treats! Make sure you share
with your friends too.
202: Well, I guess all's well that ends well.
211:
Ehehe, I got to help out, and I even
got snacks in return!
